  "title": "Chewbacca Runs the Etti IV Blockade",
  "summary": "Chewbacca pilots the Millennium Falcon toward Etti IV, ignoring all CSA hails and bulling through Corporate Sector port security commanded by Simone Drake. As Headhunter and IRD-A fighter squadrons scramble to intercept, Chewbacca outflies and outguns them, destroying an IRD and shredding an entire squadron of Headhunters before feinting a jump to lightspeed to shake his pursuers. He immediately reverts back in near the atmosphere, sets the Falcon down in a meadow near the city, and slips away on foot with his bowcaster and survival gear. Sneaking to the edge of a park, he finds the area crawling with heavily-armed ESPO guards on patrol.",
